// x,y and viewport in device pixels - we assume the view fills the screen horizontally and pixels are square
function tap(viewportX, viewportY, x, y) {
    var viewportScale = window.innerWidth / 2048
    var contentScale = 2048 / screen.width;
    var pixelScale = screen.width / viewportX;

    var tapX = (window.pageXOffset + (x*pixelScale) * viewportScale * contentScale) / 2.0;
    var tapY = (window.pageYOffset + (y*pixelScale) * viewportScale * contentScale) / 2.0;

    window.external.notify('tap ' + tapX + ' ' + tapY);
}

function doubleTap(viewportX, viewportY, x, y) {  
    var viewportScale = window.innerWidth / 1024;
    var contentScale = 2048 / screen.width;
    var pixelScale = screen.width / viewportX;

    var tapX = (window.pageXOffset + (x*pixelScale) * viewportScale * contentScale) / 2.0;
    var tapY = (window.pageYOffset + (y*pixelScale) * viewportScale * contentScale) / 2.0;
   
    window.external.notify('doubleTap ' + window.innerWidth +  ' ' + tapX + ' ' + tapY);
}

function flickLeft()
{
   window.external.notify('flickLeft ' + window.innerWidth);
}

function flickRight()
{
   window.external.notify('flickRight ' + window.innerWidth);
}

function scrollTopLeft()
{
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
}

function scrollTopRight()
{
    window.scrollTo(2048-window.innerWidth/3, 0);
}

function scrollBottomRight()
{
    window.scrollTo(2048-window.innerWidth/3, 2874-window.innerHeight/3);
}

function scrollToPoint(x, y)
{
    
    window.scrollTo(x - window.innerWidth/2, y-window.innerHeight/2);
     
}

function scrollBottomLeft()
{
    window.scrollTo(0, 2874-window.innerHeight/3);
}

function swipeLeft() {
    //cancelDraw();
     window.external.notify('Swipe ');
    document.getElementById('root').className = 'swipeLeft';
}

function swipeRight() {
    cancelDraw();
    document.getElementById('root').className = 'swipeRight';
}


var tile_width, tile_height;
var ctx;
var drawStarted;

function chunkedDraw() {

    if (global_index < global_length && !cancelDrawing) {
        bin2canvas(ctx, binary);    
        setTimeout(chunkedDraw, 50);        
        return;
    }

    // Remove teaser unless drawing was cancelled
    if (!cancelDrawing) {
        var teaserTag = document.getElementById('teaser');
        teaserTag.src = null;
        teaserTag.style.visibility = 'hidden';
    }

    var e = new Date();
    window.external.notify('done ' + (e.getTime()-drawStarted.getTime()));
}

function draw() {
    var baseTag = document.getElementById('content');   

    if(binary != "")
    {
        var header_length = binary.indexOf('!');
        var elements = binary.substr(0, header_length).split('#');
    
    tile_width = parseInt(elements[2])*2;
    tile_height = parseInt(elements[3])*2;
    }
    else
    {
        tile_width = 2048;
        tile_height = 2800;
    }

    baseTag.innerHTML += "<img id='backdrop' src='hbl/1141/2.jpg' width='" + tile_width + "' height='" + tile_height + "' />";
    baseTag.innerHTML += "<canvas id='canvas' " + 
            " style='position:absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; width:" + tile_width + "; height:" + tile_height + ";' " + 
            "width='" + tile_width + "' height='" + tile_height + "'></canvas>\n";    

    if(binary != "")
    {
    var canvas = document.getElementById('canvas');
    ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
    ctx.scale(1/8, 1/8);


    drawStarted = new Date();
    global_chunk = 0;
    global_index = 0;
    global_length = binary.length;

    setTimeout(chunkedDraw, 50);     
    }   
}

function canSwipe() {
    if (window.innerWidth < 2000) {
        return 'false';    
    }

    return 'true'; 
}

function cancelDraw() {

    window.external.notify('cancelDraw was called');

    cancelDrawing = true;
}

var gesture;
var contentElement;

function updatePanZoom() {
   
    if (window.innerWidth < 1900) {
        document.body.className = 'zoomandpan';
    }
    else 
    {
        document.body.className = 'zoom';   
    }
}

function onGestureStart(evt)
{
    updatePanZoom();        
}

function onGestureChange(evt)
{
      updatePanZoom();
}

function onGestureEnd(evt)
{
   updatePanZoom();   
}

function onPointer(evt)
{   
    if (evt.type == "MSPointerDown")
    {
        gesture.addPointer(evt.pointerId);
        
    }        
}

function onload() {

    contentElement = document.getElementById('root');
    contentElement.addEventListener('MSGestureStart', onGestureStart, false);
    contentElement.addEventListener('MSGestureEnd', onGestureEnd, false);
    contentElement.addEventListener('MSGestureChange', onGestureChange, false);
    contentElement.addEventListener('MSPointerDown', onPointer, false);
    gesture = new MSGesture();
    gesture.target = contentElement;

    window.setTimeout(draw, 500);    
    
    window.external.notify('done onload');      
}

</script>

  </div>
</body>
